headline.main: British Mined Areas Charted by U.S. Navy; Swedish Ship Sinks Off the Coast of England

lead_paragraph: The Hydrographic Office of the United States Navy issued yesterday through the Third Naval District an official charting of the positions off England and Scotland where mines are, and also where they will be laid.
